{"tid":762871,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[星辰大海]EVE Online 仰望深空，直至高處，茫茫黑夜，眾星聚首","createTime":"2018-07-31T15:42:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-06T01:14:18.000Z","uid":138995,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"d3904aff9b396ee887b348ebf408d07de5707149","tid":762871,"uid":138995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T15:42:39.000Z","msg":"新手建議先睇咗 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/378106/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/378106/page/1</a> #1 - #24 <br />\n<br />\nEVE Online 好似都好耐冇人開po討論，無論你係新手有嘢想問，定係老鬼討論配置，呢度都可以畀你暢所欲言<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n順便宣傳下公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/31/234143_c9e7ff3c1d0c4fc4085571353ce7821b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F31%2F234143_c9e7ff3c1d0c4fc4085571353ce7821b.jpg&h=df8d3510&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nPandemic HORDE是全時區的00聯盟，屬於panfam體系聯盟，招收各個時區華人<br />\n聯盟主權在對舞之域（Geminate）古斯塔斯怪。聯盟首星到jita僅需要10個跳躍，交通方便。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A：<br />\n<br />\n1.軍團是租地還是主權：是主權軍團,我們屬於HORDE的家族體系<br />\n<br />\n2.是否需要每月出勤：不強制，新人不用擔心出勤，老人軍團會引導體驗PVP樂趣<br />\n<br />\n3.軍團離吉他遠嗎，運輸是否方便：聯盟主城離吉他10跳，快遞一天內及到<br />\n<br />\n4.軍團駐地夠不夠刷，什麼怪：兔子怪，軍團和聯盟共享刷怪地盤，有多個死角。<br />\n<br />\n5.來收割的人多不多，打架方便不：在國內時區收割的不多。聯盟隊PING接到手軟<br />\n<br />\n6.軍團福利如何：入團送狂怒VNI.pvp優異玩家發小航<br />\n<br />\n7.關於戰損：T1T2護衛到T3巡洋全補覆蓋聯盟隊全部製式船。讓PVP無後顧之憂<br />\n<br />\n8.語音用什麼軟件：聯盟跟隊需要Discord和Mumble，軍團使用yy，qq和mumble，所以需要準備四個通訊軟件<br />\n<br />\n9.是否要交API：軍團內部目前不需要，入加入聯盟興趣小組和旗艦組需要API<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n加團前請加入qq群 739677872 聯繫NBI招新官<br />\n公共接待頻道：星娱乐<br />\n<br />\n歡迎各位加入我們啦!!!軍團內部氣氛很好，有問必答，不管是刷怪還是從事製造都有充足的空間~像組團PPPPVP活動啦，友好切磋機會很多，愛刷怪的朋友不用擔心沒地方刷，愛打架的朋友也不用擔心沒架打，不論是五湖四海的朋友我們都歡迎啦!!!有什麼問題可以隨便問，我會盡量幫大家解答 &gt;&lt;"},{"pid":"ed94d90fc9e4d66e950e4a9828a949c9910a4da4","tid":762871,"uid":138995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T15:46:41.000Z","msg":"push push push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5621f2265d6603b60ab4e7d6ab3fec90c725cdb0","tid":762871,"uid":138995,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T15:52:18.000Z","msg":"繼續推"},{"pid":"bc7b64754247c2ccf10e628f9084f569e0cb3607","tid":762871,"uid":138995,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T15:56:41.000Z","msg":"唔好俾佢停"},{"pid":"03379cb4844dc514db7465e121d9c4b054765469","tid":762871,"uid":138995,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T03:19:26.000Z","msg":"碌咗個一蚊入嚟"},{"pid":"d935f3f3230dbc15c45e2b834d40d3a472cb52a3","tid":762871,"uid":138995,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T05:21:09.000Z","msg":"再搵下先"},{"pid":"cf677edaa7bb0bd218b3b515ae075e21ca55aead","tid":762871,"uid":138995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T06:18:17.000Z","msg":"Pushhhhhh"},{"pid":"e8ccb34eac8094857ba60329c271f6ba202fd0ca","tid":762871,"uid":138995,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T18:23:02.000Z","msg":"X47 打交喇"},{"pid":"24d91242bb6aa375e2413faab9cbec967371d30b","tid":762871,"uid":61422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T09:51:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔得閒睇番有咩要update，所以冇開post"},{"pid":"a33cc8f6e6d3fbdcc59e9c222e1b42583383f0d4","tid":762871,"uid":46741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T18:17:40.000Z","msg":"而家係wc日日大航刷怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  最近租左3個rorqual準備挖礦，你地個度多唔多腳本"},{"pid":"42e40a2d7aab130117a1a5c9eeaac4fa86ebab5d","tid":762871,"uid":138995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T07:09:12.000Z","msg":"我個軍團會捉腳本，大部份人都係VNI刷怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3571